title: The Sims 3 Store - June 2nd, 2009
description:
This is the full compilation of all the items available on The Sims 3 Store at the time the game was/is being released.

-- All Sims3Pack files must go to the "My Documents/Electronic Arts/The Sims 3/Downloads" folder and installed using The Sims 3 Launcher.
-- All files have been "patched" with Pescado's Compressor Tool, tested in both legal and illegal copies of The Sims 3.
-- It is recommended that you block The Sims 3 Launcher from using the internet WHILE installing on a legal copy and AT ALL TIMES on an illegal one.
-- They don't work on the RELOADED leak, you can find a patch from the reloaded leak to the razor leak on ThePirateBay.
